<h2 id="think-about-dialogue-1">Think about dialogue</h2>

<ul>
  <li>What does it mean in UI design?</li>
  <li><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/speardragon/save-image-repo/main/img/image-20221010140251485.png" alt="image-20221010140251485" />
    <ul>
      <li>marriage service
        <ul>
          <li>general flow, generic – blanks for names</li>
          <li>pattern of interaction between people</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>computer dialogue
        <ul>
          <li>pattern of interaction between users and system</li>
          <li>but details differ each time</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

<h2 id="network-diagrams">Network diagrams</h2>

<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/speardragon/save-image-repo/main/img/image-20221010140305392.png" alt="image-20221010140305392" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Show different paths through system</p>
  </li>
  <li>What leads to what</li>
  <li>What happens when</li>
  <li>Including branches</li>
  <li>More task oriented then hierarchy</li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

