<ul>
  <li>Style issues:
    <ul>
      <li>platform standards, consistency: Windows vs MacOS</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Functional issues
    <ul>
      <li>cut and paste: ^C &amp; ^V</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Navigation issues
    <ul>
      <li>embedded applications</li>
      <li>links to other apps … the web</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

